snippet.title: Nomori Pre-Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Nomori is a mind-bending third-person puzzle game. Rotate portals to change your perspective, reverse the timeflow of objects to solve puzzles and explore a twisted and magical spirit world. The game is currently in pre-alpha.

Subscribe to our newsletter for updates: https://www.enchantedworks.nl/nomori/
